Subject: [PATCH] posix-timers: thread posix-cpu-timers on -rt

commit 14cbf680c340564ac33e3518bf6c110d08d93cc9 in tip.

posix-cpu-timer code takes non -rt safe locks in hard irq
context. Move it to a thread.

